g.text: Metadata schema used by the European Genome-phenome Archive (EGA) to validate
its assay metadata object. This object is intended to contain metadata about the
raw qualitative or quantitative test performed to determine any kind of
biological property of a biological sample. It can be of different types: (1)
sequencing assay [EFO:0003740] (e.g. sequence CRAM or FastQ files); and an (2)
array assay [EFO:0002696] (e.g. intensity CEL files). Further details can be
found in the EGA-metadata-schema GitHub repository
